		<td class="smallfont"><b>A different perspective on the Affliction &quot;Nerf&quot;</b></td>
		<td class="smallfont" align="right" wrap="nowrap">Post #<b><a href="showpost.php?s=aa04df70cd6993f17dc6dcc6e0f2e0cf&amp;postid=118635&postcount=1" target="new">1</a></b></td>
