	<td class="alt2" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>I disagree with you on point one.  I wear a Circlet of F-whatever.  Every single day I play I cast innumerable numbers of Malo and Slow spells.  Over the past nine months, bug or not, the amount of time it takes to cast a spell, the manner in which I pull, the mobs I can pull, tank while slowing, etc has all been heavily influenced by the focus effect Affliction Haste III.  Sony has made a change which severely alters the manner and ability with which I can do certain things.<br />
<br />
I did not acquire the item to exploit a bug or to do things I should not be able to do.  I acquiredan item and it has behaved this way for many, many months.  The manner with which the change was made (and I would argue the fact it was made at all) is yet another demonstration of Sony's blatant disregard for customer service and a fundamental lack of understanding of the game.<br />
<br />
With this in mind, I have cancelled pre-orders of LoY for my two accounts and I am considering leaving the game altogether.</p>
	
	
	
